-- Warnaco Group says CEO Gromek to retire
-- 
-- Tue Dec 13, 2011 5:33pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/12/13/us-warnacogroup-idUSTRE7BC2GK20111213

 

 (Reuters) - Clothing company Warnaco Group Inc WRC.N said chief executive Joe Gromek will retire after nearly a decade at the helm and will be replaced by Chief Operating Officer Helen McCluskey. 
 The maker of Calvin Klein underwear and Warner's bras said McCluskey will take over from 65-year-old Gromek on Feb 1, 2012. Warnaco shares of closed at $49.78 on Tuesday on the New York Stock Exchange. (Reporting by Arpita Mukherjee in Bangalore; Editing by Viraj Nair)